data.description: Welcome home to this newly remodeled ranch-style home in a sought-after neighborhood.  Inside this beautiful home, you'll find an updated kitchen, bedrooms, and bathrooms. The kitchen is a standout feature, boasting stainless steel appliances, hardwood flooring, and a stunning accent ceiling in the eat-in area. The entire home has been freshly painted, giving it a clean and inviting feel.  The attention to detail continues with new light fixtures throughout, adding a touch of style and elegance.  Step outside and enjoy the spacious fully fenced backyard, complete with a deck perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing outdoors. There's also a convenient storage shed for all your lawn care needs.  HVAC new in 2023 with all duct work throughout replaced.   All appliances are included in the sale, making this home move-in ready and hassle-free.  To provide peace of mind, the seller is offering a free 1-year home warranty. Sellers are offering 2k towards buyer's closing costs/rate buydown.
